    },
    {
      "speaker_id": "spk_4",
      "speaker_name": "Official 1 (Elder)",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Elder",
      "first_appearance_time": 277.4
    },
    {
      "speaker_id": "spk_5",
      "speaker_name": "官员2_老年",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Elder",
      "first_appearance_time": 278.2
    }
  ],
  "audio_segments": [
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_001",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 4.5,
      "end_time": 6.3,
      "text": "那朕就明示，你是户部尚书，",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_002",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 7.8,
      "end_time": 8.5,
      "text": "是吧？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_003",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 12.1,
      "end_time": 14.1,
      "text": "海瑞是哪个部的主事？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_004",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 15.5,
      "end_time": 16.4,
      "text": "回奏陛下，",
      "emotion": "Fear",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_005",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 17.3,
      "end_time": 19.7,
      "text": "海瑞是臣主管的户部主事。",
      "emotion": "Fear",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_006",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 19.9,
      "end_time": 22.1,
      "text": "海瑞的这个东西是谁拿来的？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_007",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 22.7,
      "end_time": 25.0,
      "text": "是臣，亲自到他家里拿来的。",
      "emotion": "Fear",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_008",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 25.2,
      "end_time": 26.7,
      "text": "是谁让你去拿的？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_009",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 43.6,
      "end_time": 44.4,
      "text": "哑住了？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_010",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 49.2,
      "end_time": 51.1,
      "text": "不敢说出你背后的人了？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_011",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 51.4,
      "end_time": 52.3,
      "text": "回奏陛下，",
      "emotion": "Fear",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_012",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 53.6,
      "end_time": 56.8,
      "text": "是徐阁老，叫臣去催拿贺表的。",
      "emotion": "Fear",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_013",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 57.9,
      "end_time": 61.8,
      "text": "就是在大殿之外，当着众人，叫臣去拿贺表的。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_014",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 62.1,
      "end_time": 65.1,
      "text": "好一张利嘴。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_015",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 65.9,
      "end_time": 67.9,
      "text": "现在还说是贺表。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_016",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 69.6,
      "end_time": 70.0,
      "text": "赵贞吉！",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_017",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 70.7,
      "end_time": 72.6,
      "text": "你是英雄是好汉就敢做敢认。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_018",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 73.3,
      "end_time": 76.8,
      "text": "你属下一个小小的户部主事都知道把棺材备好了。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_019",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 77.4,
      "end_time": 80.0,
      "text": "你这个当堂官的，反而连他也不如。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_020",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 86.6,
      "end_time": 87.7,
      "text": "赵贞吉。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_021",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 90.9,
      "end_time": 92.6,
      "text": "你被陈洪问住了。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_022",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 93.7,
      "end_time": 94.6,
      "text": "回奏圣上，",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_023",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 94.9,
      "end_time": 96.7,
      "text": "臣不是被陈公公问住，",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_024",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 97.4,
      "end_time": 101.1,
      "text": "而是臣不屑回答陈公公这样大逆不道之言。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_025",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 102.0,
      "end_time": 105.3,
      "text": "主子，海瑞就是这个赵贞吉指使的。",
      "emotion": "快乐",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_026",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 106.0,
      "end_time": 111.5,
      "text": "至于赵贞吉背后是谁，主子，将他交给奴婢，奴婢有办法叫他开口！",
      "emotion": "快乐",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_027",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 134.3,
      "end_time": 137.9,
      "text": "你就不想听他如何说你是大逆不道吗？",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_028",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 142.4,
      "end_time": 142.8,
      "text": "是。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_029",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 145.2,
      "end_time": 145.6,
      "text": "说。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_030",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 147.6,
      "end_time": 155.0,
      "text": "海瑞是臣的属下，他欺君，等同于臣欺君，此臣罪一。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_031",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 155.7,
      "end_time": 161.1,
      "text": "海瑞写的这个东西，是臣亲自拿来呈送给圣上的。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_032",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 162.0,
      "end_time": 166.9,
      "text": "呈送者与书写者同罪，此臣罪二。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_033",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 170.0,
      "end_time": 178.5,
      "text": "海瑞呈送上来的，是何等狂悖犯上之言，臣知与不知，由此二罪，已难逃其咎。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_034",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 179.3,
      "end_time": 187.1,
      "text": "海瑞既然备下了棺材愿意伏诛，臣无非也备下一口棺材，伏诛罢了。",
      "emotion": "Sadness",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_035",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 188.5,
      "end_time": 191.4,
      "text": "陈公公问臣是不是英雄好汉，",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_036",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 192.1,
      "end_time": 194.5,
      "text": "臣这就回陈公公的话。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_037",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 195.9,
      "end_time": 202.5,
      "text": "海瑞狂悖犯上，陈公公何以称他为英雄好汉？",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_038",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 203.8,
      "end_time": 206.1,
      "text": "海瑞既不是英雄好汉，",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_039",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 206.9,
      "end_time": 210.8,
      "text": "陈公公何以把臣也叫做英雄好汉？",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_040",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 211.4,
      "end_time": 214.9,
      "text": "陈公公这话，本就是大逆不道之言，",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_041",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 215.4,
      "end_time": 220.8,
      "text": "臣恳请皇上命陈公公收回此言，臣方可有下言陈奏。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_042",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 227.2,
      "end_time": 228.0,
      "text": "佩服了？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_043",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 230.5,
      "end_time": 234.4,
      "text": "这会儿心里一定是在想，这才是英雄好汉，是吧？",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_044",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 235.1,
      "end_time": 235.5,
      "text": "陈洪！",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_045",
      "speaker_id": "spk_3",
      "speaker_name": "Chen Hong",
      "start_time": 236.2,
      "end_time": 237.6,
      "text": "你有眼力。",
      "emotion": "Neutral",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_046",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 238.7,
      "end_time": 242.8,
      "text": "这个海瑞是英雄好汉，这个赵贞吉也是英雄好汉。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_047",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 244.0,
      "end_time": 247.9,
      "text": "你这话没有说错，而且说得极对，极对！",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_048",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 249.8,
      "end_time": 251.8,
      "text": "极对！极对！",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_049",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 258.5,
      "end_time": 263.9,
      "text": "你不知道吧？朕这一生就喜欢英雄好汉！",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_050",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 266.1,
      "end_time": 274.0,
      "text": "包括你的什么恩师、什么靠山、什么同党，是英雄好汉都站出来。",
      "emotion": "Anger",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_051",
      "speaker_id": "spk_1",
      "speaker_name": "Emperor Jiajing",
      "start_time": 274.5,
      "end_time": 276.7,
      "text": "朕都喜欢！",
      "emotion": "快乐",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_052",
      "speaker_id": "spk_4",
      "speaker_name": "Official 1 (Elder)",
      "start_time": 277.4,
      "end_time": 278.0,
      "text": "阁老",
      "emotion": "Fear",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Elder"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_053",
      "speaker_id": "spk_5",
      "speaker_name": "官员2_老年",
      "start_time": 278.2,
      "end_time": 278.8,
      "text": "阁老",
      "emotion": "Fear",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Elder"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_054",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 279.1,
      "end_time": 282.5,
      "text": "臣不是英雄好汉，臣也没有同党。",
      "emotion": "Sadness",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_055",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 284.2,
      "end_time": 288.8,
      "text": "臣是嘉靖二十一年的进士，是天子的门生。",
      "emotion": "Sadness",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_056",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 290.2,
      "end_time": 294.5,
      "text": "要说恩师，陛下就是臣的恩师。",
      "emotion": "Sadness",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_057",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 296.7,
      "end_time": 314.2,
      "text": "嘉靖二十四年，臣从翰林院出任检点，后升侍读，升巡抚，升户部尚书，一直到两个月前，升列台阁，每一步，都是皇上的拔擢。",
      "emotion": "Sadness",
      "gender": "Male",
      "age": "Middle-aged"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_058",
      "speaker_id": "spk_2",
      "speaker_name": "Zhao Zhenji",
      "start_time": 314.6,
      "end_time": 319.4,
      "text": "要说靠山，陛下就是臣的靠山。",
